# Task Manager API

A scalable Node.js backend for task manager Built with a focus on modularity and clean architecture.

## Tech Stack
- **Runtime**: Node.js (Express.js)
- **Database**: MongoDB (Mongoose ODM)
- **Caching**: Redis
- **Security**: JWT, Argon2/Bcrypt, Express-rate-limit
- **Containerization**: Docker & Docker Compose

---

## Development Setup

### Prerequisites
- [Docker Desktop](https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/)
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v18+ recommended)